cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning approach for multi-agent communication-based coordination tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). The paper also involves natural language processing and communication protocols, which could fall under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the use of recurrent neural networks suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as another possible category.
